                <h1>Discover the Tuba: The Powerful Brass Instrument</h1>
                <p>The tuba is a large brass instrument known for its deep, rich tones. It serves as the bass voice in orchestras and bands, providing harmonic foundation. Typically made of brass and shaped in a coiled form, it is played by buzzing into a mouthpiece. The tuba is essential in various music genres, enhancing both classical and contemporary pieces.</p>
